rich_message.text:
Hi friends! 👋 I’m helping my friends from another school with their research study on Stressors and Coping Strategies of College of Science Undergraduates in the Context of Post-pandemic Blended Learning.

If you’re a science major or have friends from UPD, ADMU, DLSU, UST, Adamson, Mapua, PUP, or FEU who meet the qualifications, you/they can join their Focus Group Discussion!

✅ Enrolled in a science-related course
✅ Completed at least one year of full-load coursework
✅ Experienced both onsite & online learning (Zoom, pre-recorded lectures, etc.)
✅ 18 years old or above
✅ Can speak and understand English
✅ Have access to Zoom & stable internet
🛍️ Participants will also receive Php 100 internet allowance + Php 100 Grab voucher as a token of appreciation.

Sign up here 👉 https://bit.ly/StressorsAndCoping

Let’s support them and share our experiences together!

message.text:
𝐈𝐓𝐇𝐌 𝐛𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐠𝐬 𝐡𝐨𝐦𝐞 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐛𝐢𝐠𝐠𝐞𝐬𝐭 𝐒𝐌𝐈𝐋𝐄𝐒! 🎭

The ITHM Student Council carries smiles filled with gratitude and joy as we are honored to be awarded  “𝐓𝐚𝐦𝐚𝐫𝐚𝐰’𝐬 𝐂𝐡𝐨𝐢𝐜𝐞 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐁𝐞𝐬𝐭 𝐏𝐨𝐬𝐭𝐞𝐫” in 𝐋𝐚𝐤𝐛𝐚𝐲 𝐏𝐢𝐲𝐮 𝐀𝐰𝐚𝐫𝐝𝐬! 🏆

This recognition is not just a win—it’s a tribute to Bacolod City and its MassKara Festival, a reflection of the smiles, passion, and vibrant community spirit that shine through ITHM’s mission.

Indeed, every smile wins! As we also got awarded as the “𝐖𝐢𝐭𝐭𝐢𝐞𝐬𝐭 𝐇𝐚𝐬𝐡𝐭𝐚𝐠” with the #𝐁𝐢𝐝𝐚𝐒𝐦𝐢𝐥𝐞𝐒𝐚𝐈𝐓𝐇𝐌. 🎉

Thank you to everyone who believed with smiles and voted with their hearts. 🩷💛

This is just one of the festivals ITHM brings that never fades—because here at ITHM, we are empowered through smiles. ✨

PubMat by: Akira Pagarigan
Caption by: Antonette Zaballero

Indeed, every smile wins! As we also got awarded as the “𝐖𝐢𝐭𝐭𝐢𝐞𝐬𝐭 𝐇𝐚𝐬𝐡𝐭𝐚𝐠” with the #𝐁𝐢𝐝𝐚𝐒𝐦𝐢𝐥𝐞𝐒𝐚𝐈𝐓𝐇𝐌. 🎉

Thank you to everyone who believed with smiles and voted with their hearts. 🩷💛

This is just one of the festivals ITHM brings that never fades—because here at ITHM, we are empowered through smiles. ✨

PubMat by: Akira Pagarigan
Caption by: Antonette Zaballero

message.text:
𝐈𝐓𝐇𝐌 𝐛𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐠𝐬 𝐡𝐨𝐦𝐞 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐛𝐢𝐠𝐠𝐞𝐬𝐭 𝐒𝐌𝐈𝐋𝐄𝐒! 🎭

The ITHM Student Council carries smiles filled with gratitude and joy as we are honored to be awarded  “𝐓𝐚𝐦𝐚𝐫𝐚𝐰’𝐬 𝐂𝐡𝐨𝐢𝐜𝐞 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐁𝐞𝐬𝐭 𝐏𝐨𝐬𝐭𝐞𝐫” in 𝐋𝐚𝐤𝐛𝐚𝐲 𝐏𝐢𝐲𝐮 𝐀𝐰𝐚𝐫𝐝𝐬! 🏆

This recognition is not just a win—it’s a tribute to Bacolod City and its MassKara Festival, a reflection of the smiles, passion, and vibrant community spirit that shine through ITHM’s mission.

Indeed, every smile wins! As we also got awarded as the “𝐖𝐢𝐭𝐭𝐢𝐞𝐬𝐭 𝐇𝐚𝐬𝐡𝐭𝐚𝐠” with the #𝐁𝐢𝐝𝐚𝐒𝐦𝐢𝐥𝐞𝐒𝐚𝐈𝐓𝐇𝐌. 🎉

Thank you to everyone who believed with smiles and voted with their hearts. 🩷💛

This is just one of the festivals ITHM brings that never fades—because here at ITHM, we are empowered through smiles. ✨

PubMat by: Akira Pagarigan
Caption by: Antonette Zaballero

message.text:
𝐈𝐓𝐇𝐌 𝐛𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐠𝐬 𝐡𝐨𝐦𝐞 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐛𝐢𝐠𝐠𝐞𝐬𝐭 𝐒𝐌𝐈𝐋𝐄𝐒! 🎭

The ITHM Student Council carries smiles filled with gratitude and joy as we are honored to be awarded  “𝐓𝐚𝐦𝐚𝐫𝐚𝐰’𝐬 𝐂𝐡𝐨𝐢𝐜𝐞 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐁𝐞𝐬𝐭 𝐏𝐨𝐬𝐭𝐞𝐫” in 𝐋𝐚𝐤𝐛𝐚𝐲 𝐏𝐢𝐲𝐮 𝐀𝐰𝐚𝐫𝐝𝐬! 🏆

This recognition is not just a win—it’s a tribute to Bacolod City and its MassKara Festival, a reflection of the smiles, passion, and vibrant community spirit that shine through ITHM’s mission.

Indeed, every smile wins! As we also got awarded as the “𝐖𝐢𝐭𝐭𝐢𝐞𝐬𝐭 𝐇𝐚𝐬𝐡𝐭𝐚𝐠” with the #𝐁𝐢𝐝𝐚𝐒𝐦𝐢𝐥𝐞𝐒𝐚𝐈𝐓𝐇𝐌. 🎉

Thank you to everyone who believed with smiles and voted with their hearts. 🩷💛

This is just one of the festivals ITHM brings that never fades—because here at ITHM, we are empowered through smiles. ✨

PubMat by: Akira Pagarigan
Caption by: Antonette Zaballero

message.text:
𝐈𝐓𝐇𝐌 𝐛𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐠𝐬 𝐡𝐨𝐦𝐞 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐛𝐢𝐠𝐠𝐞𝐬𝐭 𝐒𝐌𝐈𝐋𝐄𝐒! 🎭

The ITHM Student Council carries smiles filled with gratitude and joy as we are honored to be awarded  “𝐓𝐚𝐦𝐚𝐫𝐚𝐰’𝐬 𝐂𝐡𝐨𝐢𝐜𝐞 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐁𝐞𝐬𝐭 𝐏𝐨𝐬𝐭𝐞𝐫” in 𝐋𝐚𝐤𝐛𝐚𝐲 𝐏𝐢𝐲𝐮 𝐀𝐰𝐚𝐫𝐝𝐬! 🏆

This recognition is not just a win—it’s a tribute to Bacolod City and its MassKara Festival, a reflection of the smiles, passion, and vibrant community spirit that shine through ITHM’s mission.

Indeed, every smile wins! As we also got awarded as the “𝐖𝐢𝐭𝐭𝐢𝐞𝐬𝐭 𝐇𝐚𝐬𝐡𝐭𝐚𝐠” with the #𝐁𝐢𝐝𝐚𝐒𝐦𝐢𝐥𝐞𝐒𝐚𝐈𝐓𝐇𝐌. 🎉

Thank you to everyone who believed with smiles and voted with their hearts. 🩷💛

This is just one of the festivals ITHM brings that never fades—because here at ITHM, we are empowered through smiles. ✨

PubMat by: Akira Pagarigan
Caption by: Antonette Zaballero

message.text:
Narating Na ang Ikalawang Batch ng TamHunt2025 Emails! 📨✨

Mga minamahal naming aplikante, dumating na ang inaabangan ninyong sandali—naipadala na ang mga email para sa ikalawang batch ng TamHunt 2025 applicants! Huwag kalimutang silipin ang inyong inbox at pati na rin ang spam folder.💌

Taos-puso kaming nagpapasalamat sa inyong pagtitiwala at paglahok sa #TamHunt2025. Kasama kayo sa pag-usbong ng IABF Student Council, at sabik na sabik kaming makita kayo sa mga susunod na yugto ng ating biyahe. 💟🌟

#FinestKwentoEveryKanto 
#SoaringGreaterHeights

Pubmat by Anika Jianne Recto

message.text:
Narating Na ang Ikalawang Batch ng TamHunt2025 Emails! 📨✨

Mga minamahal naming aplikante, dumating na ang inaabangan ninyong sandali—naipadala na ang mga email para sa ikalawang batch ng TamHunt 2025 applicants! Huwag kalimutang silipin ang inyong inbox at pati na rin ang spam folder.💌

Taos-puso kaming nagpapasalamat sa inyong pagtitiwala at paglahok sa #TamHunt2025. Kasama kayo sa pag-usbong ng IABF Student Council, at sabik na sabik kaming makita kayo sa mga susunod na yugto ng ating biyahe. 💟🌟

#FinestKwentoEveryKanto 
#SoaringGreaterHeights

Pubmat by Anika Jianne Recto

message.text:
Narating Na ang Ikalawang Batch ng TamHunt2025 Emails! 📨✨

Mga minamahal naming aplikante, dumating na ang inaabangan ninyong sandali—naipadala na ang mga email para sa ikalawang batch ng TamHunt 2025 applicants! Huwag kalimutang silipin ang inyong inbox at pati na rin ang spam folder.💌

Taos-puso kaming nagpapasalamat sa inyong pagtitiwala at paglahok sa #TamHunt2025. Kasama kayo sa pag-usbong ng IABF Student Council, at sabik na sabik kaming makita kayo sa mga susunod na yugto ng ating biyahe. 💟🌟

#FinestKwentoEveryKanto 
#SoaringGreaterHeights

Pubmat by Anika Jianne Recto
